{"tid":885481,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人一入天水圍就feel到浸窮人味","createTime":"2018-11-01T10:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T15:39:54.000Z","uid":18679,"like":28,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2f57fb9ae77c5540752bf78b133671f1e96cdc85","tid":885481,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:51:35.000Z","msg":"一行出月台就分得到邊d住公屋 邊d住嘉湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住公屋個d個眼神好唔友善 好似驚死你知佢秘撈報比房署咁 / 睇少佢住公屋咁<br />\n女既明明返飲食/體力勞動工硬係要著到懶光鮮/少奶奶咁 又唔知自己品味差 一睇就睇得出係淘寶貨<br />\n男既清一色tee 短褲 背囊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冬天就風褸長衫長褲背囊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n皮膚黑黑瘦瘦 唔係返工就放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有聽佢地傾計既內容真係好無養分<br />\n講黎講去都係咩今個月幾多電費煤氣費交通費電話費買餸幾多錢<br />\n男既就講叫雞/大陸個老婆/打d大陸game<br />\n跟住佢地教既仔女 灌輸既價值觀都係好小家既街頭智慧<br />\n<br />\n屯門/東涌呢d屋邨區都無咁大浸味 <br />\n深水埗雖然窮 但係窮得黎唔會想掩飾自己窮<br />\n黃大仙可能有得fight下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/01/185118_458d0d9cd2a2fbbafb9ded25d5c4056f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F01%2F185118_458d0d9cd2a2fbbafb9ded25d5c4056f.png&h=ca89043e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b84fa163b85f560e88193f9c563f74412ac425f1","tid":885481,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd3499f87fdaf9eeb768017b4f6b3917cb4ac86","tid":885481,"uid":144,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:57:58.000Z","msg":"男既清一色tee 短褲 背囊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冬天就風褸長衫長褲背囊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n？？"},{"pid":"d561f86a378b2c56f670c3c7624903bf602d695c","tid":885481,"uid":1